l/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba53b100e2da9e2f1e3b214fb4574c4da199dcb","tid":1222234,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a2a581f82e182512ff651af3e98358b8f1b144","tid":1222234,"uid":82547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"推 星期日 一定要出黎"},{"pid":"f51fd7da2db5a60a219e0f06cb46a66abc7907b8","tid":1222234,"uid":48267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:30:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"004b488aea6c871eb3a1d9d370f890a93317546a","tid":1222234,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"追究暴力鎮壓責任"},{"pid":"1d91bde38f7f68d438760ed8013cd075df06a4e3","tid":1222234,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回，不僅撤回！<br />\n不撤回不散！<br />\n不放人不散！<br />\n不引咎不散！<br />\n不追責不散！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a84de21b988847072d6e8142669d77ac37ae0790","tid":1222234,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"[緊急/請廣傳] 政府暫緩以退為進，星期日香港人唔出嚟將會一敗塗地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224213\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224213</a><br />\n<br />\n經過69百萬人遊行同612血腥鎮壓，政府既管治合法性已經危在旦夕，全世界都等緊機會作致命一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家政府扮聽民意暫緩修例，目的係以退為進，買時間令善忘既香港人沖淡怒氣，同時令國際社會無機會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人因為政府暫緩而星期日唔出嚟，之後將會係連場既大規模清算同白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無人會再敢抗爭，惡法原封不動通過，69既百萬人遊行，612義士既犧牲將會毀於一旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想呢件事發生，就要趁全世界站係香港人一方，民氣最強既時候出黎遊行，堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場仗冇階段性勝利，一係贏，一係輸，winner takes all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa255f4a731d39c1cb292c4e2d01f5575b436a2d","tid":1222234,"uid":35379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"fe96029cf3f036ddc681b6a6680849029f541c27","tid":1222234,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9900ef4cf5ddd5db192c39079d1cfd3820bc781","tid":1222234,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"1b6d73ac608287237acad2c953f97fde9b248a1a","tid":1222234,"uid":196660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"大家唔好忘記<br />\n<br />\n拯救義士<br />\n停止白色恐佈<br />\n警權過大"},{"pid":"27aace9cf98e7da4ab292caeb83e9b14528a00dc","tid":1222234,"uid":12149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 永久撤回引渡方案<br />\n2. 釋放被捕義士<br />\n3. 追究暴力黑警<br />\n4. 政官問責落台</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"999d21a887217d956088dbf4b421b766362e60eb","tid":1222234,"uid":149927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b80436ed5cf32e